of mice.

00:06:41.166 --> 00:06:42.935
So here's what he does.
He has a backup plan.

00:06:42.968 --> 00:06:45.471
He has some pork that's thawing
out in his refrigerator,

00:06:45.504 --> 00:06:48.541
