conversations I had with him

00:07:50.502 --> 00:07:53.606
was in his backyard,
and he was grilling,

00:07:53.639 --> 00:07:54.974
and there was a falcon

00:07:55.007 --> 00:07:56.942
that actually lived in his
neighborhood.

00:07:56.975 --> 00:08:00.012
And it was soaring overheard,
and he was looking up at it,

00:08:00.045 --> 00:08:02.815
